    "\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "hyp = pd.read_csv('/datasets/hypotheses_us.csv')\n",
    "display(hyp.head(), hyp.info())\n",
    "\n",
    "# Validaciones\n",
    "for col in ['Reach','Impact','Confidence','Effort']:\n",
    "    hyp[col] = pd.to_numeric(hyp[col], errors='coerce')\n",
    "    assert hyp[col].between(1,10).all(), f'Valores fuera de 1-10 en {col}'\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "\n"

   "source": [
    "# 7) Dispersión del número de pedidos por usuario\n",
    "\n",
    "from statsmodels.stats.proportion import proportions_ztest\n",
    "\n",
    "# Sumas por grupo: pedidos y visitas\n",
    "agg = daily.groupby('group').agg({'orders':'sum','visits':'sum'})\n",
    "success = agg['orders'].values\n",
    "nobs    = agg['visits'].values\n",
    "\n",
    "z, p = proportions_ztest(success, nobs)\n",
    "print(f'z={z:.3f}, p={p:.4f}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 20,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",

      "U=129042, p=0.8622\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "rev_A = orders_clean.loc[orders_clean['group']=='A','revenue']\n",
    "rev_B = orders_clean.loc[orders_clean['group']=='B','revenue']\n",
    "u, p = stats.mannwhitneyu(rev_A, rev_B, alternative='two-sided')\n",
    "print(f'U={u:.0f}, p={p:.4f}')"
   ]
  },
  {

      "Conversión filtrada: z=-2.683, p=0.0073\n",

   ],
   "source": [
    "#8) Datos filtrados (sin outliers)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "ord_cut = orders_per_user.quantile(0.99)\n",
    "rev_cut = orders_clean['revenue'].quantile(0.99)\n",
    "\n",
    "valid_users = orders_per_user[orders_per_user < ord_cut].index\n",
    "orders_f = orders_clean[\n",
    "    orders_clean['visitorId'].isin(valid_users) &\n",
    "    (orders_clean['revenue'] < rev_cut)\n",
    "].copy()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Recalcular daily con filtrados\n",
    "daily_orders_f = (\n",
    "    orders_f.groupby(['date','group'])['transactionId']\n",
    "    .nunique()\n",
    "    .reset_index()\n",
    "    .rename(columns={'transactionId':'orders'})\n",
    ")\n",
    "daily_f = visits.merge(daily_orders_f, on=['date','group'], how='left').fillna({'orders':0})\n",
    "daily_f['conversion'] = daily_f['orders'] / daily_f['visits']\n",
    "\n",
    "# z-test conversión filtrada\n",
    "agg_f = daily_f.groupby('group').agg({'orders':'sum','visits':'sum'})\n",
    "z_f, p_f = proportions_ztest(agg_f['orders'].values, agg_f['visits'].values)\n",
    "print(f'Conversión filtrada: z={z_f:.3f}, p={p_f:.4f}')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Mann-Whitney AOV filtrado\n",
    "rev_Af = orders_f.loc[orders_f['group']=='A','revenue']\n",
